Help Text: Start recording vprof data for playback later.

Name: vprof_record_stop
Help Text: Stop recording vprof data

Name: vprof_remote_stop

Help Text: Reset the stats in VProf profiler

Name: vprof_reset_peaks
Help Text: Reset just the peak time in VProf profiler

Name: vprof_scope

Name: vprof_to_csv

Name: vprof_unaccounted_limit
Help Text: number of milliseconds that a node must exceed to turn red in the vprof panel

Name: vprof_verbose
Help Text: Set to one to show average and peak times

Name: vprof_vtune_group
Help Text: enable vtune for a particular vprof group ('disable' to disable)

Name: vprof_warningmsec

Name: vtune

Name: writeip
